		  <tr>
		<td width="100%" colspan="2" bgcolor="#808080" background="/images/tb_silver.gif">
		  <p align="center"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>
		  Priest of Najena</font></b><br><a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=60128" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></td>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" colspan="2" align="middle">
		    
			<BR><FONT FACE="Verdana" size="3">2 Screenshots Available!</FONT><BR><BR>
			
			</td>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" colspan="2">
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?id=87707" target="_blank">Image #1</a></font><font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;<a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?id=108234" target="_blank">Image #2</a></font>
		</td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td valign="top" width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Beast Name:</font><br></b>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">Priest of Najena&nbsp;</font></td>
		    <td valign="top" width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>
		    Location:</font><br></b>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2"><A href="../geography/default.asp?MAPID=2395">Estate of Unrest</a>&nbsp;</font>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top" rowspan="2" nowrap><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Known Level Range:</font><br></b>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">27 / 30&nbsp;</font></td>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>
		    Quest Related: </font></b>
				Yes
			 </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Magic Caster: </font></b>
				Yes
		    </td>
		    </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Faction Hits:</font></b><br>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    Faction hit with Najena
		    &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Loot:</font></b>&nbsp;
		    
		    <br>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    I have only killed it once and it had coins and a tarnished bronze key that is used in the Mystic Cloak quest
		     &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td align="middle" width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Description</font></b>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
			While named Priest of Najena it is actually found in Unrest. It was implemented as part of the Mystic Cloak quest (best cloak for caster in game). The Priest hits for 60s melee and is hard to take down because it greater heals itself big time. Looks just like a regular ghoul (would have screenshot but it is a 6-9 hour camp and Ive killed it once although ive heard others kill it) It spawns in a little 3rd floor room no bigger than a closet past the bedroom. It (or it's placeholder) are the only spawns in room. Most of the time you will get a regular ghoul
		  
		  </font>
		  </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
